    "description": "Craftsvilla Global Group, one of India's leading organizations, is hiring a E-commerce Executive for our Chandigarh operations. We offer a competitive salary package along with world-class benefits.\n\nAbout Craftsvilla Global Group:\nCraftsvilla Global Group is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Coordinate with vendors and suppliers for inventory management\n• Manage marketplace relationships with Amazon, Flipkart, and Meesho\n• Build and maintain affiliate and influencer marketing programs\n• Manage email marketing campaigns and push notifications\n• Execute digital marketing campaigns across Google, Meta, and other channels\n• Create engaging content for product pages and social media\n• Conduct competitor analysis and market benchmarking\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Ed / M.Ed from a recognized institution\n• 12-20 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in A/B Testing\n• Proficiency in SEO/SEM\n• Proficiency in Digital Marketing\n• Proficiency in Retention Marketing\n• Proficiency in Content Writing\n• Proficiency in Supply Chain\n• Proficiency in Google Analytics\n• Proficiency in Facebook Ads\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Salary Range: 35 LPA - 70 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Chandigarh, Punjab, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Craftsvilla Global Group!",
